float: none; background-color: #ffffff;\">, and there were no documented casualties.</span></p>','<p><span style=\"color: #252525; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 22.3999996185303px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: #ffffff;\">Beach No. 7 on the western coast, better known as \"Radha Nagar\" Beach, is one of the most popular beaches on Havelock and was named \"Best Beach in Asia\" by </span><em style=\"color: #252525; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 22.3999996185303px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\" title=\"Time (magazine)\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Time_(magazine)\">Time</a></em><span style=\"color: #252525; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 22.3999996185303px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: #ffffff;\"> in 2004.</span><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: -webkit-isolate; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.1999998092651px; color: #252525; font-family: sans-serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: none; color: #0b0080; white-space: nowrap; background: none;\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Havelock_Island#cite_note-2\">[2]</a></sup><span style=\"color: #252525; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 22.3999996185303px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: #ffffff;\"> Other notable beaches include Elephant Beach on the northwest coast and Vijaynagar Beach (No. 5), Beach No. 3 and Beach No. 1 on the east coast. Kalapathar is another famous beach for a pit stop.</span></p>',0,1,NULL,'2015-05-08 07:45:34','2015-05-08 07:45:34'),(143,229,'Simplicity: Styling, Makeup, Expressions','','<p>Your first assignment is to make <strong>four images</strong> of your model that present them in a fresh and natural way.&nbsp; Be sure to pay close attention to:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>expression</li>\r\n<li>body posture</li>\r\n<li>uncluttered background</li>\r\n<li>flattering light (e.g. open-shade)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Note that in this first lesson, I converted images to black-and-white in order to make them a little more \"timeless\" and to put more attention on the eyes, than on the colors around the model.&nbsp; For this assignment, you are free to choose color or monochrome - whichever you feel suits the particular situation, best.&nbsp; Keep any adjustments to a minimum, as the natural texture of the skin is important and agencies cannot use images in which the model has been altered too much or looks waxy or over-exposed.&nbsp; The more you practice with this general formula for \"testing,\" the faster you will build a portfolio of your own that generates from the agencies and models who see it.</p>\r\n<p>Good luck with this first assignment and be sure to ask if you have any questions.</p>',0,1,NULL,'2015-05-08 08:00:29','2015-05-08 08:00:29'),(144,230,'Locations, Model Direction, Lighting','','<p>Your new assignment is to shoot a model on location.&nbsp; Plan the shoot ahead of time in your mind, so you have a \"shoot-list\" ready to work from when you arrive.&nbsp; Pay attention to your model\'s clothing and the background you\'re using.&nbsp; Direct the model in, <strong>1) portraits</strong>; <strong>2) full- length</strong>; and <strong>3) small movement</strong>. Do this in ways that flatter the model.</p>\r\n<p>Once you\'ve completed your shoot and are happy with its results, upload two of your best images from each of these three categories - <strong>six photographs in total</strong> for critique and comments.</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Be creative and have fun with this assignment !</em></strong></p>',0,1,NULL,'2015-05-08 08:01:13','2015-05-08 08:01:13'),(145,231,' The \"Fashion Edge\"','','<p>Your assignment is to do a fashion shoot from concept to casting, styling to make-up and hair, and to include a beauty shot and movement shot.&nbsp; Use what you have available to you for location and cast a model if you can or a very photogenic model-hopeful.&nbsp; If she or he can collaborate with you on styling and makeup then have a plan and storyline and work together to achieve the best shoot you can. Try to find local makeup artists and stylist to collaborate with you if you can.&nbsp; Don&rsquo;t try to copy your inspiration exactly as the original will always be better based on the high level of production &ndash; just use it to inspire your own creativity.&nbsp; I can&rsquo;t wait to see what you shoot!&nbsp; Fashion is fun!&nbsp; Enjoy it!</p>',0,1,NULL,'2015-05-08 08:01:52','2015-05-08 08:01:52'),(146,232,'Lighting Techniques - Photographic Range','','<p>Your assignment is to shoot <strong>four or five images</strong> using an interior loc