nt-family: sans-serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: none; color: #0b0080; white-space: nowrap; background: none;\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bhavani_Island,_Vijayawada#cite_note-3\">[3]</a></sup></p>',6000,'2015-05-08',0,'island5.jpg','image/jpeg',6728,'2015-05-08 07:40:42',NULL,'2015-05-08 07:40:45','2015-05-08 07:40:45','USD',1,'',1,0,'','',0,1,0,'','',0,0,0,0,1,60),(74,'Historic Place ','<p>For models looking to advance their careers or just get that all-important \"foot in the door,\" a stunningly photographed portfolio or \"Book,\" is paramount. Such placed on an art director\'s desk can make or break chances with agencies, fashion magazines and advertisers.&nbsp; The same holds true for the photographer who produced it.&nbsp; Photographers who can create exciting photos of their model clients - images&nbsp;(\"Tests,\" as they\'\'re known in the industry) that showcase poise, beauty and talent - stand to advance their own careers, too.&nbsp; This online photography course shows you the way.&nbsp;&nbsp;<em><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>Includes Skype Consultation with Instructor.</strong></span></em></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','<p>Attractive models can be found the world-over and the collaboration of model and \"testing\" photographer can produce amazing portfolios that highlight talent on both sides of the camera.&nbsp; Taught by a top professional international model-turned-top-professional-model-photographer, this course will equip you with all you need for a solid start in one of the most exciting fields the photographic industry has to offer.&nbsp; This hands-on online photography course will supply you with the knowledge, skills - and confidence -&nbsp; to photograph a model portfolio with range and vision.&nbsp; Working in your own environment, using local models, makeup artists and stylists, you will learn to create the kinds of testing photographs today\'s commercial market is looking for.&nbsp; By course\'s end, you will have begun to compile your own testing portfolio of stunning model imagery - photographs that speak effectively and creativity to industry professionals - or simply to clients knocking on your own studio door.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Upon completion of this course, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\"Keep it simple\" while dealing with styling, hair, makeup and expressions</li>\r\n<li>Identify creative locations and effectively and creatively direct the models you use when you get there</li>\r\n<li>Capitalize on nuances in Light</li>\r\n<li>Apply the \"Model + Environment = Fashion Edge\" equation to create stunning portfolio images</li>\r\n<li>Effectively use lighting techniques to showcase your \"range\" as a model and fashion photographer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>What you will need:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Digital SLR or compact mirrorless camera (film is also fine, provided you are able to develop and scan your images in time to complete the assignments)</li>\r\n<li>Basic Photography Background:&nbsp; a general understanding of digital photography and the basic elements of composition and lighting</li>\r\n<li>Models:&nbsp; young photogenic friends who are willing to participate and help you learn your craft</li>\r\n<li>Interiors and Studio:&nbsp; a room with flattering available light from a window, or simple studio set-up with flash or strobe</li>\r\n<li>Computer and photo-processing software (e.g. Adobe Lightroom, Photoshop, etc.)</li>\r\n</ul>',29900,'2015-05-08',0,'pinkcity.jpg','image/jpeg',7359,'2015-05-08 07:56:38',NULL,'2015-05-08 07:56:39','2015-05-08 09:43:03','USD',1,'Incredible India',1,0,'','',0,1,0,'','',1,0,0,0,0,60),(75,'antartica tour','<p><span style=\"color: #292727; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-si