n style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>Includes Skype Consultation with Instructor.</strong></span></em></p>','<p>This introductory course in digital photography is for those needing a refresher in the \"basics\" - or for those that never fully grasped them to begin with.&nbsp; We\'ll cover how a camera works and how to make it work for you in a visually expressive way.&nbsp; We\'ll then add the digital \"layer\" of just how today\'s cameras take photography to even greater heights - beyond darkrooms filled with chemistry to digital \"darkrooms\" where creativity knows nearly no bounds.&nbsp; By the end of this 4-week adventure, you will be able to not only work those digital bells and whistles, you\'ll be able to have them \"chime\" just as you\'d like them - to create stunning photographs the digital way.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<strong>Upon completion of this course, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Understand and apply all of your camera\'s modes and controls</li>\r\n<li>Understand exposure</li>\r\n<li>Use light to best effect</li>\r\n<li>Compose images with an artistic eye</li>\r\n<li>Advance from taking \"snap shots\" to making \"Photographs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>What you will need:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>DSLR or mirrorless compact camera that possesses manual controls</li>\r\n<li>Additional lenses if you have them</li>\r\n<li>Computer with photo-processing software (e.g. Photoshop, Lightroom)</li>\r\n<li>A light but study tripod would be beneficial</li>\r\n</ul>',22900,'2015-05-08',0,'Digital_01.jpg','image/jpeg',376789,'2015-05-08 09:08:45','2015-05-08 10:02:35','2015-05-08 08:19:05','2015-05-08 10:02:35','USD',1,'',1,0,'','',0,1,0,'','',1,0,0,0,0,60),(77,'Nature photography','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #222222; text-decoration: none; outline: -webkit-focus-ring-color auto 5px; outline-offset: -2px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant: norm